                            <comment id="12978968" author="stack" created="Fri, 7 Jan 2011 21:18:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I just committed this to trunk and branch.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12978974" author="ghelmling" created="Fri, 7 Jan 2011 21:29:36 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks, Stack.  Turns out this still won&apos;t clean up region server PID files from a master initiated shutdown (stop-hbase.sh), but it&apos;s still better than what we have.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
